{"4327690": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "~調教女鬼~ 淨化巨乳地縛靈", "steam_appid": 4327690, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4327690/extras/bf1cc85e2b492d440c438c677ac20c6d.poster.avif?t=1774937673\" width=1170 height=660 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4327690/extras/bf1cc85e2b492d440c438c677ac20c6d.webm?t=1774937673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4327690/extras/bf1cc85e2b492d440c438c677ac20c6d.mp4?t=1774937673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>遊戲簡介</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >身為陰陽師的你，接下了淨化鬧鬼宅邸的委託，卻發現盤踞此地的並非普通怨靈——而是擁有豐滿肉體的巨乳地縛靈！！ <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4327690/extras/4ceda22ac5ef57522edcb80dce5a9718.poster.avif?t=1774937673\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4327690/extras/4ceda22ac5ef57522edcb80dce5a9718.webm?t=1774937673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4327690/extras/4ceda22ac5ef57522edcb80dce5a9718.mp4?t=1774937673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4327690/extras/ee28898dff12205339eba62b8b5aa824.avif?t=1774937673\" width=616 height=72 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作為陰陽師，你深知這是棘手的委託 <br>唯有通過特殊的<strong>「調教儀式」</strong>，才能一步步化解她的執念，讓她高潮到極樂世界</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4327690/extras/5aa62742e095a667252481630dbee057.avif?t=1774937673\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4327690/extras/f6a41752fcc24463d6d93636c6a104f1.avif?t=1774937673\" width=616 height=72 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>白天行動時段</strong>：前往商店購買靈具與法器、修練咒術與體術、與瞳對話建立關係</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>夜間淨化儀式</strong>：運用白天習得的咒術、器具與體術，對瞳進行深入的「調教」，逐步變成你的形狀</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>策略養成要素</strong>：合理分配時間與資源，解鎖更強力的調教手段，才能達成你想要的結局</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4327690/extras/973398f20cc68adbb48e9cadb303cdf9.avif?t=1774937673\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >淫蕩兔女郎、女僕？全套衣裝一次收集！<br>每換一套即帶來全新H表現與立繪<br>養成、調教、從羞澀到徹底墮落，好好裝飾你的小母鬼！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4327690/extras/9443196f9239165f0b38bdc8ab9afe37.avif?t=1774937673\" width=916 height=679 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>不只女鬼，連式神都不放過你！</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >讓忠誠的式神們主動獻身，陰陽調和，時時補充精力</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4327690/extras/f2d16ca2b1aa4f70aea790950d39b519.avif?t=1774937673\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay mu